				h1.articleheading.gg-backgroundcolor what is GRAVITY GIRL's skill?
				p.articletext GRAVITY GIRL isn't satisfied using her incredible cosmic powers to fight crime, she wants unravel the mysteries of space and time. Although she most frequently uses her gravity manipulation powers to fly and wallop her opponents with weapons, she is also capable of creating transmatter portals to teleport around the world. According to her notes, research indicates that this is just the beginning. Rewinding time. Interdimensional travel. Miniature black holes. Of course, GRAVITY GIRL might need your scientific expertise to explore the potential of her versatile THROW skill.

